ion" xml:lang="zh-CN">映入我眼帘的</span></p><p begin="16.291" end="20.103" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="16.291" end="16.494">Is</span> <span begin="16.494" end="16.715">e</span><span begin="16.715" end="16.939">very</span><span begin="16.939" end="17.385">bo</span><span begin="17.385" end="17.614">dy</span> <span begin="17.614" end="18.570">else</span> <span begin="18.955" end="19.215">but</span> <span begin="19.215" end="20.103">you</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">只有他人 却不见你</span></p><p begin="20.502" end="24.587" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="20.502" end="20.704">Try</span><span begin="20.704" end="20.935">na</span> <span begin="20.935" end="21.159">ge</span><span begin="21.159" end="21.363">t a</span> <span begin="21.363" end="21.713">one</span><span begin="21.713" end="21.905">-way</span> <span begin="21.905" end="22.318">tic</span><span begin="22.318" end="22.640">ket,</span> <span begin="22.640" end="22.877">but</span> <span begin="22.877" end="23.266">some</span><span begin="23.266" end="23.552">thing&apos;s</span> <span begin="23.552" end="23.914">mis</span><span begin="23.914" end="24.587">sing</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">想从这里离开 但无法释怀</span></p><p begin="24.936" end="27.883" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="24.936" end="25.276">I&apos;</span><span begin="25.276" end="25.670">m on</span> <span begin="25.670" end="26.042">my</span> <span begin="26.042" end="27.883">knees</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我双膝跪地</span></p><p begin="28.800" end="32.674" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.800" end="29.299">Lord</span> <span begin="29.299" end="30.145">please,</span> <span begin="30.522" end="31.001">Lord</span> <span begin="31.001" end="31.705">save</span> <span begin="31.705" end="32.674">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">祈求天父 求主垂怜</span></p><p begin="33.641" end="36.459" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="33.641" end="33.911">Come</span> <span begin="33.911" end="34.558">home,</span> <span begin="35.264" end="35.516">come</span> <span begin="35.516" end="36.459">here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">回家吧 回到这里</span></p><p begin="36.851" end="40.699" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.851" end="37.085">Co</span><span begin="37.085" end="37.672">me out</span> <span begin="37.672" end="37.896">and</span> <span begin="37.896" end="38.428">let</span> <span begin="38.428" end="39.223">me</span> <span begin="39.223" end="40.699">breathe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">回来见我 让我安心</span></p><p begin="41.693" end="45.529" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="41.693" end="42.536">Oh,</span> <span begin="42.828" end="43.248">let</span> <span begin="43.248" end="43.483">me</span> <span begin="43.483" end="44.472">breathe</span> <span begin="44.472" end="45.529">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我不想痛到喘不过气</span></p><p begin="46.466" end="49.242" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.466" end="46.668">Come</span> <span begin="46.668" end="47.681">home,</span> <span begin="48.007" end="48.259">come</span> <span begin="48.259" end="49.242">here</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">回来吧 回到这里</span></p><p begin="49.652" end="53.522" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="49.652" end="49.869">Co</span><span begin="49.869" end="50.424">me out</span> <span begin="50.424" end="50.641">and</span> <span begin="50.641" end="51.079">let</span> <span begin="51.079" end="52.021">me</span> <span begin="52.021" end="53.522">breathe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">让我知道你还在这里</span></p><p begin="54.418" end="58.072" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="54.418" end="54.613">Let</span> <span begin="54.613" end="54.869">me</span> <span begin="54.869" end="56.381">breathe,</span> <span begin="56.762" end="57.265">oh</span><span begin="57.265" end="58.072">-woah</span><spa